{"tid":293273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國新按摩項目　幫女性揉奶舒緩疼痛","createTime":"2017-06-22T04:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T17:07:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3968fd8d3d7d966ab76c6947ad29e239df9d3c71","tid":293273,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170621/640_066fb05b42f1fc926683f6b058a5417f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170621%2F640_066fb05b42f1fc926683f6b058a5417f.jpg&h=84abb790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">翻攝自FARLABEL BEAUTY</span></div><br />\n<br />\n據《泰國頭條新聞》微博報導，泰國「FARLABEL BEAUTY &amp; SPA」 (ฟาร์ลาเบล บิวตี้ &amp; สปา) 日前分享了一張員工幫躺在床上的女性，按摩胸部的照片，引來網友熱議。報導指出，當事人是因為做了豐胸手術，四年來開始出現疼痛等問題，才會找了體育專業出身，曾給運動員按摩過的好友幫忙，手掌大小也合適。據悉，這種幫女性按摩胸部的服務，90分鐘1390泰銖(約319港幣)。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170621/1145179/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170621%2F1145179%2F&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=107d2ee2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170621/1145179/</a><br />\n<br />\n有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pS0YKizCE-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpS0YKizCE-0&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=322bb174\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pS0YKizCE-0</a></div>"},{"pid":"d16e1a62a9cacde90560c60947436a6fcf3464b0","tid":293273,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170621/640_50c45738fae3ed6a16f1995854fc0471.jpg\" da